trans-unit.resname:

•	Any prescriptions for psychiatric or lifestyle medications (for example, diet or erectile dysfunction drugs)
•	Consults in languages other than English
•	Instant responses to inbox / message consults (consider video consults with available doctors for faster care)

• Years of experience

• Quality of experts who refer to them

• Where the expert studied and trained

• Board certification(s)

• Other professional accomplishments (such as peer reviewed publications and awards) • Thanks, votes, and recommendations from members
